snippet.title: CasinoRPG Trailer
snippet.description:
Play Now: http://casinorpg.com

Play the tables or own the strip in this Vegas-themed MMORPG that merges role-playing, tycoon, city-building and your favorite casino games.

Original music by Megan Randa (http://meganranda.com).
